				<td colspan="2"><span>Hail all,
<br />

<br />
So, had I known what I know now about religions and bards, I never would have signed on for Mith Marr.  But as it isand as things go, I'm stuck with him, and for that reason, my illusion masks are pretty much useless, since NPC's see through the illusion to my religion, and I'm KoS just the same as ever.
<br />

<br />
What I'm wondering is if there are any deity-altering items, spells or effects in the game anywhere... has anyone ever heard of anythinglike this?  I think I'd pay a great deal of plat for a Bracer of Religious Anonymity or an Agnostic Augment or something... but does anything like that exist?  Any help would be appreciated.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
